  "abstract": "Ground nut is an important oil and food crops. Among annual oilseeds, it is globally second only to soybean in cultivated area and in production. More than hundred countries groundnut and for many, the crop plays significant role in economy. Asia rank first in the world in area and in production of groundnut followed by Africa……",
